</id><title>海皇粥店結業 ｜海皇粥店創辦人指曾賤賣住宅 並用3000萬私人資金填氹</title><updated>2025-05-10T10:53:12+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T10:53:12+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337336"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337336"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3941913%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%259A%2587%25E7%25B2%25A5%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%2520%25EF%25BD%259C%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%259A%2587%25E7%25B2%25A5%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25B3%25A4%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%2585%2520%2520%2520%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E7%2594%25A83000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E6%25B0%25B9%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=cef118d98fa8e6f2d53d319ebcc0687b&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3941 ... 00萬私人資金填氹?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;￼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;【結業潮2025/執笠/開業/新舖】曾稱屬於全港首間連鎖粥店的「海皇粥店」，繼早前8個月內將旗下至少5間分店結業，陷入資金危機疑雲後，相隔不足半個月，海皇粥店所屬的海皇國際向全體員工發信指決定全綫結業，閉閉所有店舖及辦公室，將以債權人自願清盤的方式進行清盤。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基與蔡汪浩，在社交平台指出，已動用逾3,000萬元私人資金填補公司虧損，甚至連唯一的居所已賤賣，已用盡一切方法嘗試挽救公司及業務，但已無力繼續透過貸款等填補虧損問題。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;資料顯示，海皇粥店老闆蔡汪浩，曾於今年3月以約4800萬元沽出九肚山皓朗山莊洋房，但帳面卻勁賺1100萬元。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923148&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T10:53:12+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5b57dd5f67db6638e0ed9168f7ac41be</id><title>蝕讓成交｜ONE INNOVALE 1房連衣帽間戶350萬售予用家 兩年蝕近90萬離場</title><updated>2025-05-10T10:53:57+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T10:53:57+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337343"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337343"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3947216%2F%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25EF%25BD%259CONE%2520INNOVALE%25201%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%2580%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%25B8%25BD%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%2588%25B6350%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25BA%2588%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%2520%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25BF%259190%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=755e130f28480d3f7e39df4856de7245&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3947 ... 兩年蝕近90萬離場?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;私樓成交&lt;br/&gt;撰文：唐健恒&lt;br/&gt;發布時間：13小時前&lt;br/&gt;蝕讓成交｜ONE INNOVALE 1房連衣帽間戶350萬售予用家 兩年蝕近90萬離場&lt;br/&gt;▲ 蝕讓成交｜ONE INNOVALE 1房連衣帽間戶350萬售予用家 兩年蝕近90萬離場&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;美聯物業區域經理吳偉文表示，粉嶺ONE INNOVALE E座中層18室，實用面積約318方呎，屬1房連衣帽間設計。單位早前以360萬元放售後獲自用客洽購，雙方經議價後最終以350萬元易手，呎價約11,006元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;▼點擊圖片放大&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;+9&lt;br/&gt;資料顯示，原業主於2023年以約439.4萬元購入單位，持貨2年，帳面虧損約89.4萬元或約20.3%離場。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;土地註冊處資料顯示，ONE INNOVALE對上成交為E座高層22室，實用面積301平方呎，於上月初以395萬元沽出，呎價13,123元。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923149&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T10:53:57+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>45ebaea86860ff797f90394be78fe5f6</id><title>🆘負資產創22年新高 銀主盤增加 樓價上半年續尋底</title><updated>2025-05-10T10:54:30+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T10:54:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337349"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337349"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3947451%2F%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2589%25B522%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2520%25E9%258A%2580%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%2520%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%25BA%2595%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=4c758b09029863a341ea09e34bbd73f2&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3947 ...樓價上半年續尋底?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;雖然首季樓市交投不俗，但樓價繼續尋底，令最新負資產個案增至40,741宗，並創22年新高，同時間銀主盤數量也維持高位，業界預料，息口短期尚未回落，估計負資產個案將繼續上升，下半年才有所改善。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;樓價尚未止瀉，據金管局資料，今年首季負資產個案增至40,741宗，相較去年第四季末的38,389宗，按季增加2,352宗或6%，為2003年「沙士」第四季之後，近22年新高，反映負資產情況嚴重，同時較去年同期上升27%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;雖然去年第四季的負資產宗數，一度回落至約3.8萬宗水平，但首季過後卻再度重回逾4萬宗。金管局發言人指，住宅樓價於期內下跌1.7%，負資產個案上升是預期內的現象。同時負資產個案主要涉及按揭保險計劃下的貸款，按揭成數一般較高。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923150&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T10:54:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1a3d11046c8db47ce7b6f8489ffd92b1</id><title>灣仔一房私樓減至280萬沽 較高位平近4成</title><updated>2025-05-10T10:55:04+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T10:55:04+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337358"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337358"&gt;二手業主劈價吸客。中原周世康表示，灣仔維新大廈中高層F室，實用面積約256方呎，一房間隔，早前叫價350萬元，放盤僅約半個月，最終累減至280萬元成交，呎價約10,938元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：灣仔一房私樓減至280萬沽較高位平近4成 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250509%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250509190657937-0509_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=58806f3eaf978526fef4c5b40b477e9c&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923152&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T10:55:04+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3742ece5a6f8f33339b06b1d78830579</id><title>🆘投資者蔡志忠減磅 減價千萬放售會展寫字樓單位 意向呎價2萬元</title><updated>2025-05-10T10:55:44+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T10:55:44+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337367"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337367"&gt;菜蛇一邊出post撐市一邊自己出貨&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;資深投資者蔡志忠劈價放售旗下灣仔會展寫字樓單位。該物業屬海景單位，最新減價約13%以7,514萬元放售，意向呎價2萬元，較大樓高峰時期呎價下調近六成半。負責放售事宜的蔡志忠女兒、亞洲地產控股執行董事蔡家莉強調，公司並非看淡後市，今次出售是作為資產調配的換貨行動。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;蔡家莉表示，灣仔會展廣場辦公大樓33樓7室海景單位，面積3,757平方呎。該單位原意向8,641萬元放售，呎價2.3萬元，現減價逾1,127萬元，最新叫價7,514萬元，意向呎價2萬元，減幅約13%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址: 投資者蔡志忠減磅減價千萬放售會展寫字樓單位意向呎價2萬元 | 香港01 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60236943%3Futm_source%3D01articlecopy%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=07a9fe8ae1dfe9a7b590d5968b057fc2&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923154&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T10:55:44+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>03a60148b90e3863731898222464f66a</id><title>2025年5月啦，你仲未買到樓？你往後人生點算？仲要每個月硬掘交租？無女人肯同你一齊？叫雞都無錢，親戚朋友笑鳩你無樓？</title><updated>2025-05-10T10:57:45+08:00</updated><author><name>香蕉彈高</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T10:57:45+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337383"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337383"&gt;點算？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923156&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T10:57:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>0284f10fe31435bc0e6bd35904506a0b</id><title>老千KEN仔是你嗎？ 西沙撻訂 兩名兩房買家共遭殺訂50萬</title><updated>2025-05-10T11:11:01+08:00</updated><author><name>買樓唔好搞阿叔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T11:11:01+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572337545"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572337545"&gt;佢話買兩間投G&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="4" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/cry.gif"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="4" src="https://www.discuss.