gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他指，上址議價後減價25萬元，獲上車客以375萬元購入自用，呎價約6,769元。據悉，原業主於2018年以505萬元購入單位，持貨約7年易手，帳面蝕讓約130萬元離場，單位期內貶值約25.7%。&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：已補價居屋錄蝕讓三房賣375萬7年貶值逾百萬 | on.cc東網 | 產經&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250509/bkn-20250509122155186-0509_00842_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="d21b45bfc12d18368fe3dcbaf4202516"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250509/bkn-20250509122155186-0509_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31923458&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1257787680681f4f1f6c38a9_68220229"/><published>2025-05-10T17:05:42+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1e9765c95fb9ab47e940ba43bddc543a</id><title>【多相】銀主五折出貨！新樓兩房單位僅「3字頭」拍出</title><updated>2025-05-10T17:07:38+08:00</updated><author><name>新25</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-10T17:07:38+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572342637"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572342637"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16213694" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572342637" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250510/20250510_1530a4974adfa93d7869smwXBHRrRe3e.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/380eb2/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250510/20250510_1530a4974adfa93d7869smwXBHRrRe3e.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16213694_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16213694&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_b